{"tid":2285921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"室內運動又要戴返口罩 玩具撚會否猝死？？？","createTime":"2020-11-14T13:41:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T06:14:13.000Z","uid":7439,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7179005f164815b76fc911114749d49d36297051","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9p-UR34Q5S6xngE9heQY0UcPVjs=/1280x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YQ6GTRJ7LBAAPL7G2WHORX2OUE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9p-UR34Q5S6xngE9heQY0UcPVjs%3D%2F1280x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYQ6GTRJ7LBAAPL7G2WHORX2OUE.jpg&h=fb97802d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/14/P2020111400757.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F14%2FP2020111400757.htm&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=565fd443\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202011/14/P2020111400757.htm</a><br />\n政府收緊社交距離措施<br />\n<blockquote>（五）<span class=\"red\">市民在室內體育處所及公眾溜冰場運動時必須佩戴口罩</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span class=\"red\">除非</span>與另一人保持至少1.5米距離、有效間隔或進行<span class=\"red\">某些涉及較少身體接觸的運動</span>；</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202011/14/P2020111400757_354329_1_1605358857053.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgia.info.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2F202011%2F14%2FP2020111400757_354329_1_1605358857053.pdf&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=adc26714\" target=\"_blank\">https://gia.info.gov.hk/general/202011/14/P2020111400757_354329_1_1605358857053.pdf</a><br />\n在室內體育處所進行下述任何一項運動時，<span class=\"red\">毋須佩戴口罩</span>：<br />\n<blockquote>棒球、羽毛球、保齡球、板球、單車、劍擊、高爾夫球、體操、緩跑、劍道、草地滾球、桌球、運動攀登、壁球、乒乓球及網球。 </blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb9cb034ab519f9973b8cd9ff966ade8001691e7","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:41:47.000Z","msg":"政府在7月底推出「口罩令」，強制市民在公眾地方戴上口罩，及至8月底稍為放寬，容許市民於郊野公園戶外範圍及室外做運動時無需佩戴口罩，其後再容許市民在室內做運動時亦不用戴上口罩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3937cf83cadf650041ef59fff041eddbd4094245","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:43:11.000Z","msg":"香港籃球總會周一（2日）宣布，「第41屆工商盃全港籃球公開賽」<span class=\"red\">將於11月16日起以閉門形式復賽</span>，按照康樂及文化事務署（康文署）最新指引，球員無須佩戴口罩進行比賽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">明針對你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/202024106e/cgn202024106200.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gld.gov.hk%2Fegazette%2Fpdf%2F202024106e%2Fcgn202024106200.pdf&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=4a103982\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gld.gov.hk/egazette/pdf/202024106e/cgn202024106200.pdf</a><br />\n本人現行使《預防及控制疾病 ( 規定及指示 ) ( 業務及處所 ) 規例》( 第 599 章，附屬法例 F)《規例》 ( ) 第 8 條所賦予本人的權力，指示在2020 年<span class=\"red\"> 11 月 16 日起</span>至 2020 年 11 月 26 日的 11 日期間內</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e8d6736a984ce596b3dbb78aa47fb42e88947ecd","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20201102/photo/bkn-20201102152750179-1102_00882_001_02b.jpg?20201102182119\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20201102%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201102152750179-1102_00882_001_02b.jpg%3F20201102182119&h=d03e18db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滿貫大前鋒方誠義對於復賽而又不需戴口罩的消息感興奮：「不用戴口罩打波當然好，<span class=\"red\">球員戴着口罩打波會非常辛苦，易地而處，球證戴着口罩又怎樣吹哨子呢？當然，有得打波好過不能打！</span>」但「除罩」範圍只限於比賽中的10名球員和兩個落場執法裁判，意味球員被換離場後，便隨即要再配戴口罩，阿Ga對如何處置口罩有所疑問：<span class=\"red\">「換出坐低時球員定會想唞唞氣，再戴上口罩難免有影響，而且臉部的汗水又會沾濕口罩，使得口罩失效又難看，出場前後如何放置口罩也是一個問題。」</span>他建議賽會可以準備運動口罩供球員使用，以順暢比賽流程"},{"pid":"569170bc403f5677bac59753055ff3d983a5dff0","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"羽毛球唔使戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/virus_mask_20201114_feature1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2Fvirus_mask_20201114_feature1.jpg&h=b9f7d33c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2b4276f63c6c5e4680e611eb08ae907d4985f8f","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T15:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346da0cbb373f7790a643031ec3c344d3ef5bcdd","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"工商盃籃球賽再延期! 香港籃球總會剛通知傳媒，由於政府剛剛推出新的防疫指引，在室內運動場的人士要戴口罩，故此原定周一（16日）重啟的工商盃又被迫押後。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n籃總通告指出，由於進行籃球比賽時呼吸及吸氣量變大，呼氣時釋出二氧化碳，若戴口罩做運動，部份二氧化碳亦會積聚在口罩內，令人不斷吸入二氧化碳，頭暈的風險增加。運動員亦有機會邊做運動邊調整口罩，好有可能因分心或反應不及而引致意外或受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，原定於周一開始的106場賽事復賽，又要煞停。基於以上原因，香港籃球總會決定把第41屆工商盃全港公開籃球賽延期舉行。<br />\n<br />\n工商盃於1月時因疫情叫停，至7月時，又因第3波疫情押後，今次已是第3次延期。<br />\n<br />\n#本地籃球 #工商盃 #睇體<br />\n------------------<br />\n支持香港運動員，快啲去Like《睇體》個 facebook：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37yMvPZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37yMvPZ&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=42b86972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37yMvPZ</a><br />\n<br />\n再follow埋《睇體》個 IG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ontv_sports/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fontv_sports%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f6e6ce39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/ontv_sports/</a><br />\n<br />\n再再訂閱《睇體》個YouTube頻道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lD6cD7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lD6cD7&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNy1pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=45366bff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lD6cD7</a>"},{"pid":"2471c05c9102b85b71f4b1934af2837bf2783627","tid":2285921,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"挽挽具會猝死？你有無見過人砌砌下下積木猝死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ac8c12dcd9231a57f834e6d5f57f194dc6fea0","tid":2285921,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2471c05c9102b85b71f4b1934af2837bf2783627","tid":2285921,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"挽挽具會猝死？你有無見過人砌砌下下積木猝死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98480120776f5ebecc7eba0e89f752a450711b8","tid":2285921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36ac8c12dcd9231a57f834e6d5f57f194dc6fea0","tid":2285921,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2471c05c9102b85b71f4b1934af2837bf2783627","tid":2285921,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"挽挽具會猝死？你有無見過人砌砌下下積木猝死？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T19:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:32:06.000Z","msg":"砌積木唔使開冷氣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7858cac68a7b36c60dea74b48033ca3968e2001","tid":2285921,"uid":67225,"like":